00x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/rihanna_glasto_rumours-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/rihanna_glasto_rumours-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/rihanna_glasto_rumours-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>有传言说<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）</a>可能是<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">2025年格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a>的头条新闻，此前有报道称伦敦体育场在节日之后的几天出现。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="959" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/rihanna-every-album-ranked-and-rated-2921163"><b>蕾哈娜（Rihanna）：每张专辑排名和评分</b></a></li></ul><p>星期五，《 <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/news/rihanna-glastonbury-2025-lineup-rumours/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>电讯报》</i></a>报道说，“伞”明星可能计划在伦敦体育场举行六晚居留，第一次约会于7月4日下降 - 格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）今年结束了五天。</p><p>居住权尚未确认，<i>电报</i>声称“高级音乐会行业来源”表示，这些节目正处于高级计划阶段，预计未来几周的公告。</p><p> <em>NME</em>已联系蕾哈娜（Rihanna）的代表，以回应报告。</p><p>格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）迄今为止仅宣布了2025年音乐节的一个头条新闻 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-confirmed-to-headline-glastonbury-2025-after-pulling-out-3825853">尼尔·杨（Neil Young）在一月份得到了证实</a>- 传闻节目的时机特别值得注意。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825850" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825850" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825850" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="蕾哈娜（Rihanna）参加2024年时尚奖" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825850" class="wp-caption-text">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）参加2024年时装奖。信贷：Karwai Tang/WireImage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>蕾哈娜（Rihanna）从未在Worthy Farm玩过，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-57-1206280">“ Anti”世界巡回赛</a>以来就没有巡回演出，该巡回赛从2016年3月至11月进行了75场演出。当年1月发行的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/anti-track-by-track-first-listen-review-11602#:~:text=The%20pounding%20percussion%20and%20Rihanna's,and%20weave%20around%20the%20beat.">Anti</a> ”专辑仍然是她最大的最近的工作室记录。</p><p>但是，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/glastonbury-headliners-2024-rumours-bookies-3458989">长期以来一直与音乐节有关</a>，并被认为是在2023年被预订为头条新闻的，只是在怀孕后被迫拉出来，被<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">枪支玫瑰</a>所取代。</p><p>多年来，人们一直猜测这位流行巨星重返录音和巡回演出。去年夏天，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-r9-delay-starting-over-3764447">她开玩笑说，她期待着第九张专辑的漫长的等待</a>，并说她正在“重新发现事物”，并“准备回到工作室”。</p><p> “所以，我现在准备了。我要开始的，”她说。 “所以，你知道，给我一秒钟。是的，我重新开始，但我不想忽略自己的歌曲。我想用新的视角听新的耳朵的东西，然后看看仍然适用什么，我仍然爱上了什么。” </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="960" data-list-defn-props="{" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/glastonbury-2025-headliners-rumours-3773153"><b>格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2025年的头条新闻？到目前为止的顶级跑步者和骑手</b></a></li></ul><p>然而，在11月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-fuels-fan-speculation-about-future-in-music-god-had-other-plans-for-me-3811175">她在针对自己的品牌Fenty Beauty的产品发布会上发表了讲话</a>，说“音乐是吸引人的东西，但上帝对我还有其他计划，”这促使她猜测她可能决定退出音乐好的。</p><p>最后一首歌蕾哈娜（Rihanna）出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-lift-me-up-new-song-black-panther-wakanda-forever-3337860">“ Live Me Up”</a>上，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/black-panther-wakanda-forever-review-chadwick-boseman-marvel-3344219"><i>黑豹（Black Panther）的2022主打单曲：Wakanda Forever Forver</i></a> Track。她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-rihanna-powerful-performance-lift-me-up-oscars-2023-3412290">在2023年的奥斯卡颁奖典礼上表现出色</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-rihanna-play-career-spanning-set-super-bowl-halftime-show-2023-3397119">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）还在2023年超级碗半场表演中标题</a>- 这是她七年来的第一场演出。然后，她跟随去年，当时她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-plays-first-show-in-eight-years-at-billionaires-wedding-in-india-setlist-watch-footage-3595618">在八年来参加亿万富翁在印度举行的私人婚礼时，她的第一场完整表演</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832879" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832879" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832879" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="蕾哈娜（Rihanna）参加2024年的野蛮人X Fenty庆祝活动" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rihanna@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832879" class="wp-caption-text">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）参加2024年的野蛮人X Fenty庆祝活动。信贷：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images for Savage X Fenty</figcaption></figure><p>在其他新闻中，蕾哈娜（Rihanna）的合伙人<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-found-not-guilty-in-hollywood-shooting-trial-3839212">A $ AP Rocky上周因2021年的枪击事件而被判无罪</a>。洛杉矶陪审团因<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-arrested-in-connection-with-shooting-in-2021-3208779">涉嫌向他的前朋友A $ ap Relli开枪</a>而被指控罪名成立。他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aap-rocky-rejects-plea-deal-as-his-gun-trial-opens-in-los-angeles-3830874">面临24年的监禁</a>，并拒绝了一项认罪协议，监禁了180天。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-shares-statement-on-aap-rockys-gun-trial-verdict-3839304">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）对无罪释放的回应说</a>：“荣耀属于上帝和上帝！感谢他的怜悯！ <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f64f-1f3ff.png" alt="🙏🏿" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />透明</p><p>除了年轻人，迄今为止，格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2025年的其他确认名称是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-announces-rod-stewart-for-2025-legend-slot-3815832">周日下午“传奇老虎机</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rod-stewart-on-playing-glastonbury-2025-its-going-to-cost-me-a-fortune-to-do-it-3000000-3816800">”</a>的罗德·斯图尔特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nile-rodgers-chic-confirm-glastonbury-festival-2025-performance-3817280">（</a> Rod Stewart <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nile-rodgers-chic-confirm-glastonbury-festival-2025-performance-3817280">在11月的颁奖典礼上确认他们的预订</a>。</p><p>有传言称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">其他</a>许多名字还在玩<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/STEVIE-WONDER">，</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">其中</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/OLIVIA-RODRIGO">包括</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noah-kahan-announces-huge-cardiff-gig-the-same-weekend-as-glastonbury-2025-buy-tickets-3840129">·</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/alanis-morissette-announces-uk-european-tour-space-for-glastonbury-2025-3804703">卡</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">汉</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lucy-dacus-shares-new-anthem-for-queer-tenderness-best-guess-and-announces-2025-uk-and-european-tour-listen-buy-tickets-3837051">露西·达克斯（Lucy Dacus）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">售票票将在春季发售</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-tickets-sell-out-in-35-minutes-3813419">去年11月，最初的门票很快就卖光了</a>，音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-festival-2025-tickets-buy-how-to-price-line-up-faq-3809687">利用新的排队系统进行预订</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-rumoured-for-glastonbury-2025-amidst-report-of-huge-london-stadium-residency-3840361">蕾哈娜（Rihanna）曾在伦敦大型体育场居住的巨大报道中为格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）2025年的《蕾哈娜（Rihanna）</a> 》（Post Rihanna）发表在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
